			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "6.0 PRODUCTION - REQUIRED FIELDS\n\ndailyData (Chart.js input):\n  dates[] (x-axis labels)\n  series[] {\n    name (planner display name)\n    data[] (miles per date, y-axis)\n  }\n\nsummaryTable[] (bottom table):\n  planner (display name)\n  total_miles (period sum)\n  avg_per_day (total / active_days)\n  peak_miles (single day max)\n  peak_date (date of peak)\n  active_days (days with > 0 miles)\n\navailablePlanners[] (filter dropdown)\n\nscopeYearTopPlanners[] (sidebar):\n  name, total_miles (top 4 by miles)\n\nscopeYearLabel (e.g. Jul 2025-Jun 2026)\n\nFilters (user-controlled):\n  from (date), to (date)\n  planner (nullable, single select)\n  chartType (bar|line)",
			"fontSize": 12,
			"fontFamily": 3,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": "box-production-needs",
			"originalText": "6.0 PRODUCTION - REQUIRED FIELDS\n\ndailyData (Chart.js input):\n  dates[] (x-axis labels)\n  series[] {\n    name (planner display name)\n    data[] (miles per date, y-axis)\n  }\n\nsummaryTable[] (bottom table):\n  planner (display name)\n  total_miles (period sum)\n  avg_per_day (total / active_days)\n  peak_miles (single day max)\n  peak_date (date of peak)\n  active_days (days with > 0 miles)\n\navailablePlanners[] (filter dropdown)\n\nscopeYearTopPlanners[] (sidebar):\n  name, total_miles (top 4 by miles)\n\nscopeYearLabel (e.g. Jul 2025-Jun 2026)\n\nFilters (user-controlled):\n  from (date), to (date)\n  planner (nullable, single select)\n  chartType (bar|line)",
